# Project-specific
NOTES.md

# Local SQLite database: rebuilt each run, never commit the binary (caused
# push/pull merge failures). Text state in data/ (seen_dois.txt) is committed.
data/*.db
data/*.db-wal
data/*.db-shm
data/*.db-journal

analyze_floor.py

# Lineage run files and sidecars (crawls, .selection.json, .forward.json) are
# per-machine artifacts, regenerated on the laptop; never committed. *.tmp
# covers an interrupted atomic sidecar write.
runs/*.json
runs/*.tmp

# Lineage scratch files from the manual selection paste flow
reply.json
payload.txt
Inbox/Lineages/